Project Overview

This project is to develop a Python Web app functioning as a biosecurity guide, providing information on agricultural pests and weeds present in New Zealand. The Web comes with the agricultural theme which is a friendly-use interface that contains three different user roles and access control: Agronomists, Staff and Administrator.

Aim

Understand and learn the permissions of different users.
